claim.claim-text:
A flexible display device, comprising:
a first body (210);
a second body (220) configured to move relative to the first body (210) between a first position and a second position in a first direction;
a support (230) aligned in a second direction orthogonal to the first direction and coupled to the second body (220);
a flexible display (300) comprising a first region (310), a second region (320), and a third region (330), wherein the first region (310) is fixed in front of the first body (210); and
a plurality of cameras (122) located at a rear of the first body (210) and toward an edge of the flexible display device away from the support (230), wherein the plurality of cameras (122) are arranged along the second direction,
wherein when the second body (220) is at the first position a distance from the support (230) to an end of the third region (330) is greater than or equal to a distance from the support (230) to a center of one of the plurality of cameras (122).
